                            <comment id="12668508" author="shalinmangar" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2009 16:33:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to log the name of the file (SolrConfig.xml in this case) and then re-throw the exception.&lt;/p&gt;

